channel.title: Objects.cfg
channel.description:
Hello,
I'm using a cheezscape source (update 80)
and when I start up, it says config/objects.cfg not found.
I downloaded the file from the internet, and created a folder named config and placed it in there, and when I ran the server it still didn't work.
I tried recompiling a million times but the server wouldn't recognize it. I placed it in the cfg folder as well, but nothing happened.
Is there anyway to fix this?
